<section class="why-uberflip">
    <div class="container">
        <h2>Why Uberflip?</h2>
        <p class="sub-heading">The most powerful way to connect with your audience is through a compelling content marketing experience.<br>Uberflip empowers marketers to create that experience and leverage their content to drive growth.</p>
    
        <div class="row">
            <div class="span4">
                <div class="why-tile-layout">
                    <div class="why-uberflip-icon control"></div>
                    <p class="title">More Control</p>
                    <p>Forget the IT department - as a marketer, you need to regain control of your resources page and the entire content experience!  Uberflip gives you the ability to create a killer content experience and manage it from A to Z.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="span4">
                <div class="why-tile-layout">
                    <div class="why-uberflip-icon insights"><span></span></div>
                    <p class="title">Better Insights</p>
                    <p>Despite the plethora of analytics tools available, there is still a black hole when it comes to measuring content performance.  Uberflip closes the gap by feeding key insights into your marketing automation tool for better audience segmentation and targeting.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="span4">
                <div class="why-tile-layout">
                    <div class="why-uberflip-icon growth"><span></span></div>
                    <p class="title">Faster Growth</p>
                    <p>Let's face it, traditional resources pages and blogs are not designed with conversion in mind.  Uberflip is designed for lead generation, turning your content marketing engine into an effective tool for driving business growth.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
            
